    <entry>
      <title>Markdown 的数学公式</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/09/Markdown-%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/09/Markdown-%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>写在前面的话</strong><br>本文会不断的记录在写 Markdown 时, 用到的数学公式符号, 会不断的保持更新。</p><h1 id="Markdown-数学公式的使用"><a href="#Markdown-数学公式的使用" class="headerlink" title="Markdown 数学公式的使用"></a>Markdown 数学公式的使用</h1><ul><li>行内公式：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$公式$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>行间公式：<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">公式</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><h1 id="LaTeX-的常用数学符号"><a href="#LaTeX-的常用数学符号" class="headerlink" title="LaTeX 的常用数学符号"></a>LaTeX 的常用数学符号</h1><h2 id="数学运算符号"><a href="#数学运算符号" class="headerlink" title="数学运算符号"></a>数学运算符号</h2><ul><li>点乘, 如 $a \cdot b$<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \cdot b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>叉乘, 如 $a \times b$ <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \times b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>除以, 如 $a \div b$<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \div b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>求和, 如 $\sum_{a}^{b}{c}$<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\sum<span class="emphasis">_&#123;a&#125;^&#123;b&#125;&#123;c&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">$$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>积分, 如 $\int_{a}^{b}{c}$<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\int<span class="emphasis">_&#123;a&#125;^&#123;b&#125;&#123;c&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">$$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>累乘, 如 $\prod_{a}^{b}{c}$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\prod_&#123;a&#125;^&#123;b&#125;&#123;c&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>分数, 如 $\frac{a}{b}$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\frac&#123;a&#125;&#123;b&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>偏导数符号, 如 $\partial$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\partial</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="数学关系符号"><a href="#数学关系符号" class="headerlink" title="数学关系符号"></a>数学关系符号</h2><ul><li>大于等于, 如 $a \geq b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \geq b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>小于等于, 如 $a \leq b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \leq b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>相似于, 如 $a \sim b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \sim b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>两条竖线, 如 $a \parallel b$<br>(<font color=green>暂时不知道代表什么数学概念</font>)<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \parallel b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>约等于, 如 $a \approx b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \approx b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="希腊字母"><a href="#希腊字母" class="headerlink" title="希腊字母"></a>希腊字母</h2><ul><li>$\phi$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\phi</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>$\mu$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\mu</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>$\gamma$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\gamma</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>$\varepsilon$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\varepsilon</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>$\varphi$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\varphi</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>$\lambda$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\lambda</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="空格"><a href="#空格" class="headerlink" title="空格"></a>空格</h2><font color=green>暂不清楚什么时间应用什么空格</font><ul><li>空格距离：3/18 em, 如 $a \, b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \, b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>空格距离：4/18 em, 如 $a \: b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \: b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>空格距离：5/18 em, 如 $a \; b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \; b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>空格距离：1 em, 如 $a \quad b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \quad b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>空格距离：2 em, 如 $a \qquad b$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">a \qquad b</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>注：em 是指当前文本的<strong>字体尺寸</strong></p><h2 id="数学字体"><a href="#数学字体" class="headerlink" title="数学字体"></a>数学字体</h2><p><strong>花体</strong></p><ul><li>花体：<code>\mathcal</code>, 如</li><li>$\mathcal L$ (<code>\mathcal L</code>) 常用来表示损失函数</li><li>$\mathcal D$ (<code>\mathcal D</code>) 表示样本集</li><li>$\mathcal N$ (<code>\mathcal N</code>) 常用来表示高斯分布</li></ul><p><strong>空心</strong></p><ul><li>空心：\mathbb, 如 $\mathbb R$ 、$\mathbb N$</li></ul><h2 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h2><p><strong>LaTex 把下标放在正下方</strong></p><ul><li>如果是数学符号, 那么直接在 <code>_</code> 前加 <code>\limits</code> 命令, 即可把符号放在正下方, 如 $\sum \limits_{a}^{b}{c}$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\sum \limits_&#123;a&#125;^&#123;b&#125;&#123;c&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>如果是普通符号, 那么要用 <code>\mathop</code> 先转成数学符号再用 <code>\limits</code>, 如 $\mathop{max} \limits_{a, b}$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\mathop&#123;max&#125; \limits_&#123;a, b&#125; </span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>对于<strong>双美元符</strong>之间的公式, LaTeX <font color=red>默认下标放在正下方</font></li></ul><p><strong>LaTex 字符上面加符号</strong></p><ul><li><p>加 ^, 如 $\hat{a}$ 或 $\widehat{a}$<br>$\hat{a}$</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\hat&#123;a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\widehat{a}$</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\widehat&#123;a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>加横线, 如 $\overline{a}$</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\overline&#123;a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>加波浪线, 如 $\widetilde{a}$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\widetilde&#123;a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>加一个点, 如 $\dot{a}$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\dot&#123;a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>加两个点, 如 $\ddot{a}$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\ddot&#123;a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><strong>单个公式换行</strong></p><ul><li><p>单个公式很长的时候需要换行, 在<strong>需要转行的地方</strong>使用 <code>\\</code>, 每行需要使用 1 个 <code>&amp;</code> 来标识对齐的位置, 如：</p><!-- $$\begina &= b \\bc &= d \\def &= g\end$$ --><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{align}a &= b \\cc &= dd \\eee &= fff \end{align}</script><p>代码示例：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\begin&#123;align&#125;</span><br><span class="line">a &amp;= b \\</span><br><span class="line">cc &amp;= dd \\</span><br><span class="line">eee &amp;= fff </span><br><span class="line">\end&#123;align&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$$ </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：<code>align</code> 是基本的对齐环境</p></li></ul><p><strong>范数</strong></p><ul><li>二范数, 如 $\Vert W \Vert_2 = 1$<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\Vert W \Vert_2 = 1</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>(<font color=green>暂不清楚 \left 和 \right 的含义</font>)<br>另一种写法：<font color=red>但是在 hexo 上不可行</font><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\left \| W \right \|_2 = 1</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>绝对值, 如 $\vert W \vert = 1$<br>(这里是<strong>小写的 v</strong>)<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\vert W \vert = 1</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
